OL,3,CNewcastle Hospitals trust 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' amid bullying allegations
OL,6,FNewcastle upon Tyne Hospitals NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust has been downgraded
OL,8,Ffrom "outstanding" to "requires
OL,9,Fimprovement" following inspections by
OL,10,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC).
OL,12,FSome staff told inspectors they were
OL,13,Fworried about raising concerns with
OL,14,Fbosses and others reported that
OL,15,Fbullying at work was routine.
OL,17,FThe CQC undertook unannounced
OL,18,Finspections at the trust, which runs
OL,19,Fthe Royal Victoria Infirmary, the
OL,20,FFreeman Hospital and other sites, last
OL,21,Fsummer.
