OL,3,CNewcastle Hospitals trust 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' amid bullying allegations
OL,6,FA second, targeted inspection took
OL,7,Fplace in the cardiothoracic surgery
OL,8,Fdepartment at the Freeman Hospital in
OL,9,FSeptember, following whistleblowers'
OL,10,Fclaims about bullying, harassment and
OL,11,Fsafety concerns.
OL,13,FFollowing this inspection, the overall
OL,14,Frating for the trust dropped from
OL,15,F"outstanding" to "requires
OL,16,Fimprovement".
OL,18,FThe CQC rated how well-led the trust
OL,19,Fwas as "inadequate" falling from its
OL,20,Fprevious rating of "outstanding."
