OL,6,FSafety has dropped from "good" to
OL,7,F"requires improvement" while caring
OL,8,Fhas dropped from "outstanding" to
OL,9,F"good".
OL,11,FThe CQC said the trust must make
OL,12,Fspecific improvements within a
OL,13,Ftimeframe and submit monthly reports
OL,14,Fto show what progress has been made.
OL,16,FThe trust has vowed to make
OL,17,Fimprovements set out in the report as
OL,18,Fa matter of urgency.
OL,20,F'Significant deterioration in how well
OL,21,Fthe trust was being led'
