OL,3,CNewcastle Hospitals trust 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' amid bullying allegations
OL,6,FAnn Ford, CQC's director of operations
OL,7,Fin the north, said: "When we visited
OL,8,Fthe Newcastle upon Tyne Hospitals NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust, we found a
OL,10,Fsignificant deterioration in how well
OL,11,Fthe trust was being led.
OL,13,F"Our experience tells us that when a
OL,14,Ftrust isn't well-led, this has a knock-
OL,15,Fon effect on the standard of services
OL,16,Fbeing provided to people.
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@AOU
