OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F422A1706217257
OL,3,CNewcastle Hospitals trust 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' amid bullying allegations
OL,6,F"We found leaders had the skills and
OL,7,Fabilities to run the trust but they
OL,8,Fweren't using them to always manage
OL,9,Fthe priorities and issues they faced
OL,10,Fin a timely way.
OL,12,F"Also, the board had a lack of
OL,13,Foversight at all levels to effectively
OL,14,Fmanage and reduce risks to people.
OL,16,F"We were also concerned to hear the
OL,17,Ftrust didn't have an open culture
OL,18,Fwhere staff could raise concerns
OL,19,Fwithout fear of blame or punishment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
