OL,3,CNewcastle Hospitals trust 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' amid bullying allegations
OL,6,F"Some staff told us that bullying was
OL,7,Fa normal occurrence, and they were
OL,8,Fencouraged to 'turn a blind eye' and
OL,9,Fnot report this behaviour.
OL,11,F"This is completely unacceptable and
OL,12,Fmust be addressed by the leadership
OL,13,Fteam as a priority to enable staff to
OL,14,Fprovide the best possible experience
OL,15,Fto people."
OL,17,FMs Ford praised staff for the care
OL,18,Fprovided and trust employees said they
OL,19,Fwere proud to work there.
