OL,6,FShe added: "Inspectors also found some
OL,7,Foutstanding practice.
OL,9,F"For example, in children and young
OL,10,Fpeople's services at both hospitals,
OL,11,Fstaff were exceptional in supporting
OL,12,Ffamilies and loved ones to understand
OL,13,Fa child's condition and they knew when
OL,14,Fto escalate concerns, so the child
OL,15,Freceived appropriate care as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible."
OL,18,FSince the inspections, Dame Jackie
OL,19,FDaniel has stepped down as chief
OL,20,Fexecutive and Sir James Mackey has
OL,21,Ftaken over.
