OL,6,FAccepting the CQC's findings, he said:
OL,7,F"Everybody is very disappointed."
OL,9,FSir James said the report's
OL,10,Frecommendations are being worked on
OL,11,F"as a matter of urgency" and he is
OL,12,Fconfident matters can be resolved and
OL,13,Fimproved.
OL,15,FHe said: "A detailed programme of
OL,16,Factivity is already underway and will
OL,17,Fcontinue until we, and the CQC, are
OL,18,Fassured the issues have been addressed.
