OL,6,F"This will involve some tough
OL,7,Fdecisions but it's important we get
OL,8,Fthis right and that people can see
OL,9,Fchange happening.
OL,11,F"Of course, it is a huge
OL,12,Fdisappointment that our overall rating
OL,13,Fhas been reduced and to hear of the
OL,14,Fdifficulties experienced by some
OL,15,Fcolleagues.
OL,17,F"I know from speaking to many staff
OL,18,Fover the last few weeks that providing
OL,19,Fthe best possible patient care remains
OL,20,Fan absolute priority for everyone at
OL,21,FNewcastle Hospitals.
