OL,6,F"While this is a challenging time,
OL,7,Fit's important to emphasise that the
OL,8,Finspectors saw and highlighted the
OL,9,Fcompassion and kindness of our teams
OL,10,Fand rated 'caring' as 'good'."
OL,12,FSir James said staff would be
OL,13,Fencouraged to speak up as he addressed
OL,14,Fthe bullying allegations.
OL,16,F"We want to make sure that people can
OL,17,Ffeel confident that when they raise
OL,18,Fissues, they will be dealt with
OL,19,Fappropriately," he said.
